* Iron Raptor sighed, maybe a checkup at the labs would finally find out 
what was going on with her. Maybe....
She nodded as Prowl slid his hand around her waist, leaning against him as 
he instructed.
Iron Raptor leaned her head against Prowls shoulder as then began to walk 
towards his quarters, hoping that Dinobot would be alright while they were 
gone.
Besides, she had left the computer on alert, if anything went wrong, she 
would know about it.
Iron Raptor leaned harvier against Prowl, the sick feeling in her head and 
stomach slightly intensifying.*
